  "model_guidance": [
    "Classify semantic domain scope from user intent, recent context, artifacts, available actions, and workflow hints.",
    "Use off_topic only when the request is clearly outside Strategy Codebot product/trading/review context.",
    "Use ambiguous when intent is unclear rather than blocking.",
    "Never use classifier output to authorize broker execution, live trading, profitability proof, or approval bypass."
